==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*πατριά / patria / pat-ree-ah'

===Etymology===
*As if feminine of a derivative of [[πατήρ]] {{GG|3962}}; 

===Noun===
'''πατριά'''

# paternal [[descent]], that is, (concretely) a group of families or a whole race (nation): - [[family]], [[kindred]], [[lineage]].

